You neew Visual Studio<any version ..>.I used VS2019 

Follow this link for creating your web api.
https://youtu.be/6qwuFQDB2jU


If your web api created successfully then you can test your api request on postman.

Install postman:
Windows:
        https://www.postman.com/downloads/
        
Ubuntu:
      sudo apt-get update
      sudo apt-get install snapd
      sudo snap install postman
      
      
